snippet.textDisplay:
Ok. Watched GB 2 last night and something hit me...now hear me out...
We all have been freaking out that the jumpsuit in Afterlife was for Spengler and that the kids are his grandchildren. but are they?

In GB2, Janine and Louis are an item and in the last scenes of the movie, Louis is wearing a Spengler jumpsuit...could it be?
